original_title: Delmark Records: 55 Years Of Blues Performance Collection
overview: Ten live blues performances in Chicago clubs, released to celebrate Delmark Records' 55th anniversary. Tail Dragger, Jimmy Burns, Lurrie Bell, Carey Bell, Byther Smith, Dave Specter, Little Arthur Duncan, Mississippi Heat, Zora Young & more.
title: Delmark Records: 55 Years Of Blues Performance Collection
